+---[ 0: README ]-----------------------
|   Installing:
|     Go to your occa directory
|     You should see:
|        include, src, lib
|
|     type "make"
|
|     Setup environment variables (1)
+=======================================


+---[ 1: ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES ]--------
|  Required environment variables:
|    (2) OCCA_DIR
|
|  Optional environment variables:
|    (3) OCCA_MPI_ENABLED
|    (4) OCCA_OPENCL_ENABLED
|    (5) OCCA_CUDA_ENABLED
+=======================================


+---[ 2: OCCA_DIR ]---------------------
|  Info:
|    Directory where occa/ is stored:
|      $OCCA_DIR/include
|      $OCCA_DIR/src
|      $OCCA_DIR/lib
|
|  Setting it:
|    export OCCA_DIR=/absolute/path/to/dir (note: no end / after dir)
+=======================================


+--[ 3: OCCA_MPI_ENABLED ]--------------
|  Info:
|    Enable MPI features in OCCA
|
|  Enabling MPI features:
|    export OCCA_MPI_ENABLED=1
|
|  Defaults to:
|    export OCCA_MPI_ENABLED=0
+=======================================


+--[ 4: OCCA_OPENCL_ENABLED ]-----------
|  Info:
|    Enable OpenCL mode in OCCA
|
|  Enabling OpenCL:
|    export OCCA_OPENCL_ENABLED=1
|
|  Defaults to:
|    export OCCA_OPENCL_ENABLED=0
+=======================================


+--[ 5: OCCA_CUDA_ENABLED ]-------------
|  Info:
|    Enable CUDA mode in OCCA
|
|  Enabling CUDA:
|    export OCCA_CUDA_ENABLED=1
|
|  Defaults to:
|    export OCCA_CUDA_ENABLED=0
+=======================================
